{"tid":774608,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本推出漢字模型      砌得到東京和大阪","createTime":"2018-08-10T12:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T01:49:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":95,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"55d653258064157523878131049828ddee8a41a0","tid":774608,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/jpn-06_yYbCU_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fjpn-06_yYbCU_1200x0.png&h=b73f6091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日係網上睇到呢隻手辦模型，未知係砌咩就已經見到大隻字「東京」同「大阪」。原來一款係砌東京鐵塔，全高約14mm；另一款係砌大阪城！動手之前，已經先比個包裝設計吸引。想砌同時又唔捨得拆個包裝，每款仲有要藍色、紅色、螢光三款選擇，即係要我一款買幾個，日本人賺錢真係有一手！<br />\n<br />\n有時都幾慶幸中國漢字傳到日本，到當地落生根之餘，仲一直係漢字設計上發揚光大。 早前去完PMQ個「漢字展」（展期：2018 年 6 月 21 日 &ndash; 2018 年 7 月 10 日），單係嚟自日本的漢字海報設計，已叫人心生讚嘆。今次漢字直程跳出平面設計，再揉合到模型設計之中。先睇得，再砌得，唔知幾時直情可以食得。食字咁食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/4580397-90902-6-4_5KGws_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F4580397-90902-6-4_5KGws_1200x0.jpg&h=01c4f207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/4580397-90902-6-g_EFaA0_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F4580397-90902-6-g_EFaA0_1200x0.jpg&h=be22f9d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/art/%E6%BC%A2%E5%AD%97-x-%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E7%A0%8C%E5%BE%97%E5%88%B0%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%A7%E9%98%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fart%2F%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%25AD%2597-x-%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%259E%258B-%25E7%25A0%258C%25E5%25BE%2597%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%259D%25B1%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2598%25AA%2F&d=idlRQUqkF3qAdBQ7IAyxffM6KyiA14vjm6